{"code":0,"data":[{"cid":63742,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":10851,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"我国传统文化家的意识太强，老人从生活还是心理都依赖子女的话对双方都不好，希望有更多类似老年社区的东西形成老人社群","timestamp":1593431807,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":63751,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":10851,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"只能期待社会保障能越来越好。如果儿女在身边城市还好，如果儿女在其他城市打拼，996，emmm。。。","timestamp":1593431909,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":63752,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":10851,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Alice: 赞同","timestamp":1593431917,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":63757,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":10851,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"我希望以后自己在国外安顿好后把父母接过去养老","timestamp":1593432002,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":63759,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":10851,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"感觉现在的子女即使对老人很好，普遍的态度也是好好享福就好，不要给自己添乱","timestamp":1593432012,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":63768,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":10851,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"同意楼上。和老人拴在一起的家庭真的很那个，尤其是那种固执而傲慢的老人。","timestamp":1593432107,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":63770,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Eve","permissions":["report"],"pid":10851,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"在日本就有很多老年人独自生活，我老了以后也想独自生活","timestamp":1593432129,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":63771,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":10851,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"我是dave，dbq我说的是同意Alice","timestamp":1593432141,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":63915,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Francis","permissions":["report"],"pid":10851,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"不想等到老，我活到中年就够